posting_body: Want more information on this unit?
This is a 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 1130 Sq.
Welcome to your new home at Indigo Springs.
Located in a cozy neighborhood in Kent, WA, just southeast of Seattle.
This is an ideal apartment community for anyone working in the Seattle area with a lot of shopping and dining options in the immediate area.
In our fantastic 3, 2, and 1-bedroom apartment homes, you’ll find a number of beautiful aesthetic touches and convenient features.
Enjoy spacious floor plans with ample storage, large closets, and custom cabinetry.
Select apartments also feature premium touches, such as upscale flooring, glass style back-splash, and large decks or patios.
You’ll also find fireplaces and in-unit washers and dryers for your comfort and convenience.
$500 Pet Deposit per pet ($250 admin, $250 refundable)
